(function(){const e={zh:["重要的不是你是什么样的人，而是你做了什么。<br>It is not so important who you are, but what you do.<br>——Sönke Ahrens","活着，如同生命最后一天般活着；学习，如同永远活着般学习！<br>——圣雄甘地（印度国父）","这些（监狱的）围墙很有趣——起初你痛恨它；然后你逐渐习惯它；足够长时间后，你开始依赖它...这就是体制化！<br>——电影《肖申克的救赎》"],ja:["想像力は知識よりも重要だ！<br>知識は有限だが、想像力は世界のすべてを包含し、進歩を促し、知識進化の源泉だ。<br>——アインシュタイン","人はみなオリジナルとして生まれる。悲しいことに、多くの人が次第にコピーになっていく。","ほとんどの人は考えるよりも死ぬことを選ぶ。実際、彼らは死ぬまで考えない。<br>——バートランド・ラッセル（哲学者・数学者・思想家）"],en:["It is not so important who you are, but what you do.<br>——Sönke Ahrens","Live as if you were to die tomorrow. Learn as if you were to live forever.<br>——Mahatma Gandhi","These prison walls are funny. First you hate them, then you get used to them. Enough time passes, you depend on them... That's institutionalized!<br>——The Shawshank Redemption"]};function n(){let e=document.documentElement.lang;return e?e.startsWith("zh")?"zh":e.startsWith("ja")?"ja":e.startsWith("en")?"en":"en":"en"}function t(){const o=n(),t=e[o]||e.en,s=document.getElementById("quote");if(s&&t.length>0){const e=t[Math.floor(Math.random()*t.length)];s.innerHTML=e}}document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded",t),window.InstantClick&&InstantClick.on("change",t)})()